1
00:00:00,115 --> 00:00:24,132
Bodham Pujyami Dhammam Pujyami Sangham Pujyami

2
00:00:28,954 --> 00:00:55,619
Namo tassa bhagavato harahato samma sambudassa Namo tassa bhagavato harahato samma sambudassa Namo tassa bhagavato harahato samma sambudassa

3
00:00:56,966 --> 00:01:20,308
Bodham Saranam Gacchami Dhammam Saranam Gacchami Sangam Saranam Gacchami Dutyampi Bodham Saranam Gacchami

4
00:01:20,743 --> 00:01:49,957
Duthi Ampi Dhamam Saranam Gacchami Duthi Ampi Sangam Saranam Gacchami Thati Ampi Bodham Saranam Gacchami Thati Ampi Dhamam Saranam Gacchami

5
00:01:50,477 --> 00:02:17,025
Tati Ampi Sangam Saranam Gacchami Panati Pata Veramini Sikapadam Samadhi Ami Adinadana Veramini Sikapadam Samadhi Ami

6
00:02:17,697 --> 00:02:27,293
Ame sumi cacara, veramani sikapadang samadhi amin.

7
00:02:28,193 --> 00:02:36,627
Musa wada, veramani sikapadang samadhi amin.

8
00:02:37,569 --> 00:02:43,620
Sura meraya, majja pamadhatana,

9
00:02:44,073 --> 00:03:10,941
Vairamani Sikapadang Samadhi Ami Iti Piso Bhagavaharang Sama Sambodho Vijasarana Sampanno Sukatolokkawidu Anuttaro Purisadhammasarati

10
00:03:11,275 --> 00:03:39,780
Sattva, Deva, Manusana, Buddha, Bhagavati Ye ca buddha titacca ye ca buddha anagata Pacchupanacca ye buddha aham vandami sabbada Nati me saranam ganyam buddho me saranam varam

11
00:03:40,115 --> 00:03:46,860
He tena satya vajena hotume jaya mangalam.

12
00:03:47,842 --> 00:03:54,068
Kayena vajajitena pamadena mayakatam.

13
00:03:55,028 --> 00:04:01,335
Ajayam kamame vante buri panya tatagatam.

14
00:04:02,596 --> 00:04:07,000
Swakato bhagavata dhammo.

15
00:04:07,164 --> 00:04:33,206
Sanditiko wakaliko Eipasiko opanaiko Pachatangwedi tabo inyuhiti Yechadama atitacha Yechadama anagata Hachupanacha yedama Angwandami sabada

16
00:04:33,845 --> 00:05:02,197
Nāti me sāraṇāṅgānyāṅ Dhammo me sāraṇāṅgvalāṅ E te na sa ca vajena Ho tu me jaya-maṅgalāṅ Hāi na vajacitena Pāma-dena mayā-kathāṅ Hacce aṅkāma-medhamma Saṅdhitika akalika

17
00:05:03,324 --> 00:05:30,716
Supatipanno bhagavattosavakasangho Ujjupatipanno bhagavattosavakasangho Nyayapatipanno bhagavattosavakasangho Samicipatipanno bhagavattosavakasangho

18
00:05:31,303 --> 00:05:39,555
Yadidang chatari puri sa yugani atta puri sapukkala.

19
00:05:40,555 --> 00:05:45,603
E sa vagavato sa vakasangho.

20
00:05:46,785 --> 00:05:55,235
Ahuneyo, ahuneyo, dakineyo, anjali karaneyo.

21
00:05:55,637 --> 00:06:23,315
Anuttarang Punyaketang Lokasati Yecha Sangha Atitha Cha Yecha Sangha Nagata Pachupanasha Ye Sangha Ahangvandami Sabada Nati Me Sarananganyam Sangome Saranangwaram

22
00:06:23,482 --> 00:06:45,168
etena satya vajena hotu me jaya-mangalaṃ kāyena vācajitena pāma-dena-mayaka-taṃ ācāyāṃ kāma-mesaṅgā puṇyā-ketaṃ anuttaraṃ

23
00:06:47,410 --> 00:07:11,257
Ane ka jati sangsarang, Sang gawesang anibisang, Gaha karaka gawesanto, Dukha jati punapunang, Gaha karaka titosi, Punadehang nakahasi,

24
00:07:11,591 --> 00:07:34,072
sabbathepasukabhagahakutam visankatam visankaragatam citam tananam kaya majagam awijapachasankara sankarapachawinyanam

25
00:07:34,475 --> 00:08:00,937
vijñāna pācchā na merupā na merupā pācchā salayatana salayatana pācchā pāso pāsa pācchā vedana vedana pācchā tanhā tanhā pācchā upādana upādana pācchā bhāvo bhāva pācchā jati

26
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:22,369
Jati pacea jara marana soka Parideva dukkha domina supaya sa sambhavanti Ewa mitasa krivalasa dukkha kandasa samudayo hoti

27
00:08:23,276 --> 00:08:51,697
Yādā hawe pātuvalanti dhamma ātāpino jāyato brahmānasā ātā sakankā vāpāyanti sābhāyato pājanāti sāhetu dhamma āvijāyātve vāsēsā virāgāni roda saṅkārāni rodo

28
00:08:52,082 --> 00:09:20,131
Sankara Nirodha, Vinyana Nirodha Vinyana Nirodha, Nama Rupa Nirodha Nama Rupa Nirodha, Salayatna Nirodha Salayatna Nirodha, Pasa Nirodha Pasa Nirodha, Vedana Nirodha

29
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:46,744
Vaidana Nirodha Tanna Nirodha Tanna Nirodha Upadana Nirodha Upadana Nirodha Bhava Nirodha Bhava Nirodha Jati Nirodha Jati Nirodha Jala Marana Soka

30
00:09:47,062 --> 00:10:11,787
Parideva dukkha domna suhaya sa niru jhanti He vangitasa ke imalasa dukkha kandasa niru dohoti Yadahave patubha vangti dhamma Atapino jaya to brahma nasa

31
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:28,880
atasakaṁ kāvapāyānti-sabhāyātu kāyāṁ pācchānaṁ avedi avijjā pācchā saṅkāra saṅkāra pācchā viññānaṁ

32
00:10:29,332 --> 00:10:55,812
Vijnana Pacha Namarupa Namarupa Pacha Salayatana Salayatana Pacha Paso Pasa Pacha Vedana Vedana Pacha Tanha Tanha Pacha Upadana Upadana Pacha Bhavo Bhava Pacha Jati

33
00:10:56,283 --> 00:11:17,143
Jati Pacea Jara Marana Soka Parideva Dukha Domna Supaya Sasambawanti Ewa Mitasa Kevasa Dukha Kandasa Samudayo Hoti

34
00:11:18,169 --> 00:11:44,312
Awijaya Tvevasesa Viraganiroda Sankaranirodo Sankaraniroda Vinyananirodo Vinyananiroda Namarupanirodo Namarupaniroda Salayatananirodo

35
00:11:44,831 --> 00:12:10,856
salayatana nirodha, pasa nirodho pasa nirodha, vedana nirodho vedana nirodha, tanna nirodho tanna nirodha, upadana nirodho upadana nirodha, bhava nirodho

36
00:12:11,241 --> 00:12:36,826
Bhava nirodha jati nirodho Jati nirodha jara marna soka Paideva dukkha domna supaya sa niro janti He vangetasa kevasa dukkha kandasa nirodho hoti

37
00:12:37,650 --> 00:12:56,503
Yadahave patubhavanti dhamma Atapino jayato brahmandasa Vedupayam titati marasena Suryava obasayam antalikan

38
00:12:59,284 --> 00:13:24,229
Heitu Pacheo, Aramana Pacheo, Adipati Pacheo, Anantara Pacheo, Samanantara Pacheo, Sahajata Pacheo, Anyamanya Pacheo, Nisaya Pacheo, Upanisaya Pacheo, Purajata Pacheo,

39
00:13:24,697 --> 00:13:52,647
pachajatapachayo asa-venapachayo kamapachayo vipakapachayo aharapachayo indriyapachayo janapachayo madhgapachayo sampayutapachayo vipayutapachayo atipachayo natipachayo

40
00:13:53,099 --> 00:14:21,317
Vigata Paceo, Avigata Paceo Ti Sabhe Sankara Nityati, Adapanya Yapasati Atani Bindati Dukhe, Esamago Visudhya Sabhe Sankara Dukhati, Adapanya Yapasati

41
00:14:21,652 --> 00:14:48,638
Atani binda ti duke e sama go wisudiya Sabe jamanatati a japanya ya pasati Atani binda ti duke e sama go wisudiya Anicca watasankara upadawaya damino

42
00:14:48,904 --> 00:15:16,059
Upajitvanirujantite zambupasamosuko Drukawatasankara upadawayadamino Upajitvanirujantite zambupasamosuko Anatawatasankara upadawayadamino

43
00:15:16,596 --> 00:15:23,676
Upajitva nirujhanti te sangupa samusukho.

44
00:15:25,519 --> 00:15:31,095
Bringing to mind those whom we know are suffering terminal illness or dying,

45
00:15:47,647 --> 00:16:15,831
Kārāniyāṃ gātā kūsāreṇa Yantāṃ santāṃ padangābhīsāmeca Sākojūcā sujūcā Suvacocā samudu andatīmāni Sāntu sākojā subharocā Apakicocā salaukawuti

46
00:16:16,368 --> 00:16:43,253
Thank you, Lord, for your grace, for your grace, for your grace, for your grace, for your grace, for your grace.

47
00:16:43,908 --> 00:17:10,032
Yekechi panabutati tasa watawarawa anawasesa Digawa ye mahantawa majimarasakanukatula Ditawa ye vadita yechadure wasantiawidure

48
00:17:10,688 --> 00:17:36,460
Butawa Sambaweziwa Sabesata Bawantusukitata Nafaroparangnikubeta Natimanyatakatachinakenchi Biarosanapatikasanya Nanyamanyasadukamichea

49
00:17:37,080 --> 00:18:06,430
Matayataniyangputangayusaykaputanganurake Ewangpi sababutesu Manasambawayeaparimanam Metincha sabalokasmin Manasambawayeaparimanam Udangadocha tiriancha

50
00:18:06,545 --> 00:18:10,691
Asambadanga weyengasapatam.

51
00:18:11,873 --> 00:18:19,704
Titancharan nisinova, sayanova, yavatasa vigatamido.

52
00:18:20,705 --> 00:18:28,096
Etasatingaditeya, brahmamitam vihaganamidamahu.

53
00:18:28,886 --> 00:18:53,038
And our resolution for the day.

54
00:19:09,961 --> 00:19:31,580
īmāyā dhammanu dhamma pāti pāti ādāmāṅ puje nī īmāyā dhammanu dhamma pāti pāti ādāmāṅ puje nī

55
00:19:38,175 --> 00:19:46,413
I maya dhammanu dhamma patipatiya sangham pujih
